io.elegie.luchess.core.api.explore

Interface GameListQueryResult

  • All Superinterfaces:
    QueryResult
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GameListQueryResultImpl, TimedGameListQueryResult

    public interface GameListQueryResult
extends QueryResult
    Returns the page of games, matching the criteria specified in the query. Statistical data about possible continuations are also included.
